WEBVTT

00:00:13.367 --> 00:00:20.207 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the whole of humankind,
Be sure you’ll never find

00:00:20.207 --> 00:00:26.297 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Someone who can say,
“I’ve never stumbled in my life.”

00:00:26.297 --> 00:00:32.678 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And now this time it’s you,
But there’s something you can do:

00:00:32.678 --> 00:00:41.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Learn from the experience,
And take the help our loving God provides.

00:00:41.562 --> 00:00:48.068 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Get back up when you’re down.
You can turn this around.

00:00:48.068 --> 00:00:54.325 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Get back up; stand up tall.
You can learn from a fall.

00:00:54.325 --> 00:00:57.578 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Just reach out;
take his hand.

00:00:57.578 --> 00:01:01.040 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He’ll raise you up—
make you stand.

00:01:01.040 --> 00:01:09.131 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And one thing that’s for sure:
You’ll be stronger than before

00:01:09.131 --> 00:01:14.178 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If you learn from a fall.

00:01:24.271 --> 00:01:30.235 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Another dawn is breaking,
And your heart may be aching.

00:01:30.235 --> 00:01:36.700 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
